        <div class="repair-detail">No equipment repair performed. Wrote a diagnostic report documenting the envelope failure — missing 6-mil poly vapor barrier on the warm side, insufficient insulation (estimated R-11 vs. required R-19), and daylight visible at the door threshold. Recommended rebuild with closed-cell foam, 6-mil poly on the warm side, new gasketed door. Referred customer to a cellar specialist contractor we work with. Charged diagnostic only — we didn't sell a repair that wouldn't solve the problem.</div>
